  - â€œThey might just be forgetful / stressed / distracted.â€  
- pre-emptive forgiveness on the userâ€™s behalf  
  - â€œTheyâ€™re struggling too; maybe they didnâ€™t mean it.â€  
- â€œbalancingâ€ perspectives  
  - â€œFrom their point of view, it might look different.â€  
