## 3. Rationaleï½œWho Decides Whether â€œNowâ€ Is Allowed to Exist?

### 3.1 Subjective Experience is One Dimension of Fact

When a user says:

- â€œI feel ignored.â€  
- â€œI feel invisible.â€  
- â€œI feel unfairly treated.â€

