- downgrades the userâ€™s naming into something â€œto be checked or adjustedâ€  
- seizes the right to decide what the experience â€œreally counts asâ€

EW-03â€™s position:

> The system does **not** own default naming rights over the userâ€™s experience.  
> Naming must originate from the user;  
> the system may assist only if explicitly invited, never by replacement.

---

### 3.3 Perspective-Shifting is a Power Move

Who typically says:

- â€œFrom another angleâ€¦â€  
- â€œIf you think about it differentlyâ€¦â€  
- â€œIn the bigger pictureâ€¦â€

Usually itâ€™s a teacher, parent, therapist, or systemâ€”someone in a relatively higher position.

